## fcon1000.csv
Contains cortical thickness and brain volumes from structural MRI

## openneuro_main.csv
Cortical thickness and subcortical volume data used to demonstrate the main workflow. These are derived from OpenNeuro datsets ds003568 and ds003653

## openneuro_lifespan_txfr.csv
Cortical thickness and subcortical volume data used to demonstrate the transfer learning workflow. These are taken from three different OpenNeuro datasets, namely ds003469, ds003826 and ds000222

## LNM_data.csv
Cortical thickness and subcortical data from the paper: [Rehak-Buckova et al 2025](https://elifesciences.org/articles/95823). This is used for evaluating the longitudinal normative modeling pipeline.